headline: Dover Fueling Solutions Launches ProGauge LR120 Radar to Enhance Accuracy and Visibility in Industrial Applications
summary: Dover Fueling Solutions ("DFS"), a part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a leading global provider of advanced customer-focused technologies, services and solutions in the fuel and convenience retail industries, today announced the launch of the ProGauge® LR120 Radar, DFS's latest automatic tank gauging (ATG) solution specifically designed for industrial applications.
